java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
org.springframework.boot.web.client.ClientHttpRequestFactorySettings
Record Components:

@Deprecated(since="3.4.0", forRemoval=true) public record ClientHttpRequestFactorySettings(Duration connectTimeout, Duration readTimeout, SslBundle sslBundle) extends Record
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
since 3.4.0 for removal in 4.0.0 in favor of ClientHttpRequestFactorySettings
Settings that can be applied when creating a ClientHttpRequestFactory.
